summary:
My Account - Information about user account features like orders, wish list, profile, and password.

 Checkout - Information about new products, designers, prevention products, clothing, shoes, accessories, beauty, our story, press, and sale.

 Designers A-Z - List of designers alphabetically from 0-9 to Q-Z.

 Featured Designers - List of featured designers and their products like shoes, accessories, clothing, prevention products, and beauty items.
